263
00:40:27.175 --> 00:40:29.385
Daemon and rhaenyra
were seen together...

264
00:40:31.512 --> 00:40:33.598
In the bowels of a pleasure den.

265
00:40:44.901 --> 00:40:46.110
Coupling.

266
00:40:54.243 --> 00:40:55.870
This is a lie.

267
00:40:56.871 --> 00:40:58.498
You have been lied to.

268
00:40:59.457 --> 00:41:01.459
I only wish that were true. your grace.

269
00:41:03.711 --> 00:41:05.713
Who is responsible for this gossip?

270
00:41:06.881 --> 00:41:09.342
Have this rumormonger
brought before me at once.

271
00:41:09.425 --> 00:41:11.427
And I will take their eyes.

272
00:41:11.511 --> 00:41:15.098
As your hand. I must maintain trusted
sources of information.

273
00:41:15.181 --> 00:41:17.892
And this one. as yet.
has never led me astray.

274
00:41:18.643 --> 00:41:21.980
And several of the servants
have now admitted to seeing her.

275
00:41:22.063 --> 00:41:24.065
the Princess...

276
00:41:24.148 --> 00:41:26.401
Creeping through the gates
from king's landing.

277
00:41:26.484 --> 00:41:28.319
disguised as a page

278
00:41:28.403 --> 00:41:30.405
during the hour of the owl.

279
00:41:31.990 --> 00:41:34.158
Are you so sick with ambition

280
00:41:34.242 --> 00:41:35.994
that you would have my daughter stalked?

281
00:41:36.744 --> 00:41:38.371
Spied upon?

282
00:41:38.955 --> 00:41:42.083
Awaiting your best chance
to destroy her reputation?

283
00:41:43.001 --> 00:41:45.837
I have no such intent. your grace.

284
00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:47.922
You think yourself a cunning man.

285
00:41:49.007 --> 00:41:50.466
Your designs are obvious.

286
00:41:52.176 --> 00:41:54.512
Do you wish to have your blood
on the iron throne so badly

287
00:41:54.595 --> 00:41:56.973
that you are willing
to destroy mine own?

288
00:41:59.434 --> 00:42:00.643
Just get out.

289
00:42:04.689 --> 00:42:07.316
Leave me... at once.

290
00:42:12.613 --> 00:42:14.032
Your grace.

291
00:42:54.405 --> 00:42:56.491
I'm dressed. annora. Come.

292
00:43:06.626 --> 00:43:07.794
Princess.

293
00:43:13.591 --> 00:43:14.717
Come.

294
00:43:24.435 --> 00:43:27.105
Pdncess. lhave
a message from the queen.

295
00:43:51.712 --> 00:43:53.422
What happened last night?

296
00:43:55.174 --> 00:43:56.717
What do you mean?

297
00:43:56.801 --> 00:43:59.929
My father has made
some worrying allegations about you.

298
00:44:02.849 --> 00:44:04.016
Were you with your uncle?

299
00:44:06.769 --> 00:44:08.604
Oh. I...

300
00:44:08.688 --> 00:44:10.398
I haven't seen him in years.

301
00:44:10.481 --> 00:44:12.000
He took me into the city for some fun.

302
00:44:12.024 --> 00:44:14.277
Tell me the whole of it. rhaenyra.

303
00:44:14.360 --> 00:44:16.362
Your father accused me of something.

304
00:44:17.405 --> 00:44:19.407
That I drank wine?

305
00:44:19.490 --> 00:44:21.868
Left the castle after dark?

306
00:44:21.951 --> 00:44:23.953
That you fucked daemon
in a pleasure house.

307
00:44:32.670 --> 00:44:36.924
This is a vile accusation.

308
00:44:37.008 --> 00:44:38.050
Is it?

309
00:44:38.134 --> 00:44:41.053
You targaryens do have queer customs.

310
00:44:41.137 --> 00:44:44.307
- And daemon certainly knows no limit.
- Alicent...

311
00:44:44.390 --> 00:44:46.976
Your grace. sister.
you must know I would.

312
00:44:47.059 --> 00:44:48.394
I would never.

313
00:44:48.477 --> 00:44:49.937
You cannot believe such gossip.

314
00:44:50.021 --> 00:44:51.230
My father is no gossip.

315
00:44:51.314 --> 00:44:52.541
Well. certainly he's been misled.

316
00:44:52.565 --> 00:44:53.917
He could not have
witnessed such a thing.

317
00:44:53.941 --> 00:44:55.610
- Why not?
- Because it did not happen.

318
00:44:55.693 --> 00:44:57.695
- He was told that you...
- Told?

319
00:45:00.156 --> 00:45:02.158
Who made these claims to your father?

320
00:45:06.037 --> 00:45:08.039
I am the Princess.

321
00:45:08.748 --> 00:45:11.751
To question my virtue
is an act of treason.

322
00:45:14.086 --> 00:45:16.839
- I do not know specifically...
- Your father did not tell you?

323
00:45:17.506 --> 00:45:19.008
He reported it to the king.

324
00:45:22.303 --> 00:45:23.512
I overheard.

325
00:45:27.516 --> 00:45:29.936
So you are accusing me of slanders...

326
00:45:30.937 --> 00:45:32.563
You overheard?

327
00:45:33.356 --> 00:45:35.524
I only want to help you. rhaenyra.

328
00:45:44.325 --> 00:45:45.993
We drank in a tavern.

329
00:45:47.578 --> 00:45:50.206
Several... taverns.

330
00:45:51.290 --> 00:45:53.167
It was getting late...

331
00:45:53.834 --> 00:45:55.461
And I asked to go home.

332
00:45:56.462 --> 00:45:58.464
But daemon wished to continue.

333
00:46:01.175 --> 00:46:03.636
As he was my escort.
I had no real choice.

334
00:46:03.719 --> 00:46:05.012
"Continue"...

335
00:46:07.723 --> 00:46:08.933
In a brothel?

336
00:46:10.017 --> 00:46:12.019
He took me to a show. Uh...

337
00:46:13.813 --> 00:46:16.816
I was only a spectator.
I didn't do anything.

338
00:46:22.363 --> 00:46:25.324
And then
daemon sank into his cups and...

339
00:46:26.867 --> 00:46:30.496
Abandoned me for some whore.

340
00:46:35.001 --> 00:46:37.003
I should've known better.

341
00:46:43.092 --> 00:46:44.552
So you did not?

342
00:46:47.555 --> 00:46:50.182
Must I truly refute that?

343
00:46:54.061 --> 00:46:56.647
Daemon never touched me.

344
00:46:58.441 --> 00:47:02.486
I swear this to you
upon the memory of my mother.

345
00:47:05.823 --> 00:47:07.908
It was foolish of you to place
yourself in a position

346
00:47:07.992 --> 00:47:10.244
where your virtue could
even come into question.

347
00:47:14.206 --> 00:47:16.167
The king has strived
to find you a good match.

348
00:47:16.250 --> 00:47:17.668
And so have I.

349
00:47:18.544 --> 00:47:20.755
If that lord were to think
that you had been...

350
00:47:22.548 --> 00:47:23.758
Sullied...

351
00:47:25.426 --> 00:47:27.845
- It would ruin everything.
- I know...

352
00:47:28.637 --> 00:47:29.722
Your grace.

353
00:47:31.640 --> 00:47:32.808
I regret it.

354
00:47:48.115 --> 00:47:50.576
The king demands an audience. my prince.

355
00:47:50.659 --> 00:47:53.329
Take your fucking hands off me.

356
00:48:41.168 --> 00:48:42.336
My daughter.

357
00:48:49.844 --> 00:48:51.262
Won't you even deny it?

358
00:48:52.513 --> 00:48:56.392
I need to understand the charge
before I can attempt to discredit it.

359
00:48:57.685 --> 00:48:59.019
You defiled her.

360
00:49:07.945 --> 00:49:09.363
Still. you say nothing.

361
00:49:09.447 --> 00:49:11.657
Oh. what does it matter. brother?

362
00:49:11.740 --> 00:49:12.992
When we were rhaenyra's age.

363
00:49:13.075 --> 00:49:14.952
we fucked our way
through most of the brothels

364
00:49:15.035 --> 00:49:16.537
on the street of silk.

365
00:49:16.620 --> 00:49:18.539
We were young men.

366
00:49:18.622 --> 00:49:20.541
She is just a girl.

367
00:49:20.624 --> 00:49:22.835
- Your niece!
- Rhaenyra's a woman-grown.

368
00:49:22.918 --> 00:49:25.337
Better her first experience
be with me than some whore.

369
00:49:25.421 --> 00:49:26.422
You fucking...

370
00:49:28.132 --> 00:49:29.467
You have ruined her!

371
00:49:30.509 --> 00:49:32.428
What lord will wed her now?
In this condition?

372
00:49:32.511 --> 00:49:35.264
Who gives a fuck what some lord thinks?

373
00:49:35.347 --> 00:49:39.435
You are the dragon.
Your word is truth and law.

374
00:49:39.518 --> 00:49:42.021
I have spent a lifetime defending you.

375
00:49:42.605 --> 00:49:45.065
But your heart is even blacker
than I thought.

376
00:49:45.149 --> 00:49:47.026
I should disinherit her

377
00:49:47.109 --> 00:49:49.737
as I already did you
and be done with it.

378
00:49:50.821 --> 00:49:52.239
Wed her to me.

379
00:49:53.782 --> 00:49:56.994
When I offered up my crown.
you said I could have anything.

380
00:49:57.077 --> 00:49:59.371
I want rhaenyra.
I'll take her as she is.

381
00:49:59.455 --> 00:50:01.415
and wed her in the tradition
of our house.

382
00:50:02.541 --> 00:50:03.792
You are already wed.

383
00:50:03.876 --> 00:50:06.545
That didn't stop aegon the conqueror
from taking a second wife.

384
00:50:07.296 --> 00:50:08.923
You are no conqueror.

385
00:50:09.006 --> 00:50:12.551
You are a plague... sent to destroy me.

386
00:50:12.635 --> 00:50:15.471
Give me rhaenyra to take to wife

387
00:50:15.554 --> 00:50:17.473
and we will return
the house of the dragon

388
00:50:17.556 --> 00:50:19.308
to its proper glory.

389
00:50:19.391 --> 00:50:20.643
Of course.

390
00:50:20.726 --> 00:50:23.145
It's not my daughter
you lust for. is it?

391
00:50:24.230 --> 00:50:25.481
It's my throne.

392
00:50:28.108 --> 00:50:30.611
Go back to the vale. daemon.

393
00:50:30.694 --> 00:50:32.696
to your lawful wife.

394
00:50:33.614 --> 00:50:38.577
Strive to restore whatever
scrap of honor remains in you.

395
00:50:38.661 --> 00:50:41.580
Or don't. Matters not to me.

396
00:50:42.122 --> 00:50:44.542
As long as you are gone
from my sight for good.

397
00:50:52.007 --> 00:50:54.009
As you wish. brother.

398
00:51:24.164 --> 00:51:25.916
Have you spoken to her?

399
00:51:34.842 --> 00:51:37.469
It is not in rhaenyra's
nature to be deceitful.

400
00:51:38.721 --> 00:51:40.723
I cannot say the same for your brother.

401
00:51:41.640 --> 00:51:43.058
You believe he lied?

402
00:51:44.226 --> 00:51:46.437
How often does he speak the pure truth?

403
00:51:47.771 --> 00:51:50.774
How does confessing
to such things serve him?

404
00:51:53.652 --> 00:51:55.529
By reducing you.

405
00:52:01.660 --> 00:52:05.080
Whatever transpired.
rhaenyra is not innocent.

406
00:52:06.081 --> 00:52:08.500
Only because daemon
tried to corrupt her.

407
00:52:08.584 --> 00:52:11.837
Daemon and rhaenyra
share the blood of the dragon.

408
00:52:11.920 --> 00:52:13.714
They are restless and chaotic.

409
00:52:13.797 --> 00:52:16.634
She swore to me
that she remains a maiden.

410
00:52:18.260 --> 00:52:19.887
And I believe her.

411
00:53:24.076 --> 00:53:27.746
That dagger once belonged
to aegon the conqueror.

412
00:53:29.289 --> 00:53:31.291
It was aenar's before that.

413
00:53:32.126 --> 00:53:33.752
And before that...

414
00:53:34.586 --> 00:53:36.588
Well. it is difficult to know.

415
00:53:42.261 --> 00:53:46.223
Before aegon's death.
the last of the valyrian pyromancers

416
00:53:46.306 --> 00:53:47.725
hid his song in the steel.

417
00:53:55.524 --> 00:53:57.609
"From my blood...

418
00:53:58.277 --> 00:54:01.530
Come the prince that was promised...

419
00:54:03.615 --> 00:54:07.244
And his will be
the song of ice and fire."

420
00:54:11.582 --> 00:54:15.085
The responsibility I have handed to you.

421
00:54:15.169 --> 00:54:17.379
the burden of this knowledge...

422
00:54:18.547 --> 00:54:22.050
It is larger than the throne. the king.

423
00:54:22.134 --> 00:54:23.677
It is larger than you

424
00:54:23.761 --> 00:54:25.888
and your desires.

425
00:54:30.476 --> 00:54:32.936
Jaehaerys would've disinherited you.

426
00:54:33.020 --> 00:54:34.229
For a lie?

427
00:54:35.606 --> 00:54:38.275
You've yet to ask me for the truth
of what happened.

428
00:54:38.358 --> 00:54:40.861
The truth does not matter. rhaenyra.

429
00:54:40.944 --> 00:54:42.821
Only perception.

430
00:54:42.905 --> 00:54:44.656
You have exposed yourself.

431
00:54:44.740 --> 00:54:46.784
Now we must both
suffer the consequences.

432
00:54:47.326 --> 00:54:50.287
Were I born a man.
I could bed whomever I wanted.

433
00:54:51.288 --> 00:54:52.956
I could father a dozen bastards.

434
00:54:53.040 --> 00:54:55.751
and no one in your court
would blink an eye.

435
00:54:55.834 --> 00:54:59.087
You are right...
But you were born a woman.

436
00:55:00.088 --> 00:55:02.966
So you'll strip me of my titles
and name aegon in my stead.

437
00:55:03.050 --> 00:55:04.134
I would.

438
00:55:05.093 --> 00:55:07.346
But it is mine
to hold the realm together.

439
00:55:07.429 --> 00:55:09.264
not sow it with further division.

440
00:55:11.099 --> 00:55:13.727
Your courtship is at an end.

441
00:55:13.811 --> 00:55:16.021
You will wed ser laenor velaryon.

442
00:55:16.104 --> 00:55:18.440
and you will do so without protest.

443
00:55:19.566 --> 00:55:21.527
The son of the sea snake.

444
00:55:21.610 --> 00:55:24.112
So I can be a remedy
for your political headaches.

445
00:55:24.196 --> 00:55:26.490
You are my political headache!

446
00:55:31.286 --> 00:55:33.539
Your wedding to ser laenor velaryon

447
00:55:33.622 --> 00:55:36.166
will unite the two most powerful houses
in the realm.

448
00:55:36.250 --> 00:55:40.546
With the combined strength
of our shared dragons and naval fleets.

449
00:55:40.629 --> 00:55:43.298
no one would dare to stand against us.

450
00:55:43.382 --> 00:55:44.716
The house of the dragon

451
00:55:44.800 --> 00:55:47.261
will stand as one
for a further generation.

452
00:55:47.344 --> 00:55:51.181
And what will you do about the vulture
who perches upon your throne?

453
00:55:51.682 --> 00:55:53.058
What vulture?

454
00:55:53.642 --> 00:55:54.935
Your hand.

455
00:55:56.562 --> 00:56:00.732
Otto hightower has served two kings
onally and faithfully.

456
00:56:01.900 --> 00:56:03.902
He wants aegon to be named heir.

457
00:56:04.528 --> 00:56:07.155
And he will stop
at nothing to see it done.

458
00:56:07.239 --> 00:56:10.242
Including spying on me
to bring about my ruin.

459
00:56:11.660 --> 00:56:14.246
You speak of the conqueror's vision

460
00:56:14.329 --> 00:56:17.583
and the need for strength
and unity across the realm.

461
00:56:17.666 --> 00:56:19.293
But how can that be accomplished

462
00:56:19.376 --> 00:56:21.920
with your most trusted adviser
so self-interested?

463
00:56:22.004 --> 00:56:24.464
Every lord and lady that calls
for an audience with me.

464
00:56:24.548 --> 00:56:26.383
every man on my small council.

465
00:56:26.466 --> 00:56:29.428
and all councils past.
has been self-interested.

466
00:56:29.511 --> 00:56:31.972
- It is unavoidable.
- I disagree.

467
00:56:32.055 --> 00:56:36.059
I will do my duty as heir
and wed ser laenor.

468
00:56:38.562 --> 00:56:41.315
But you must first do yours as king.

469
00:56:52.743 --> 00:56:53.827
Your grace.

470
00:56:56.538 --> 00:56:57.748
Five days.

471
00:57:01.084 --> 00:57:03.045
I'm sorry. your grace?

472
00:57:03.128 --> 00:57:04.728
Though it was some time ago.

473
00:57:05.589 --> 00:57:08.467
The details... they fade in memory.

474
00:57:09.593 --> 00:57:12.971
My father was a hale and healthy warrior
and dragonrider

475
00:57:13.055 --> 00:57:15.057
at the peak of his abilities.

476
00:57:15.766 --> 00:57:17.476
Jaehaerys named a great royal hunt

477
00:57:17.559 --> 00:57:19.811
to celebrate him being
named the hand of the king.

478
00:57:21.939 --> 00:57:25.067
Five days later my father lay dead.

479
00:57:27.361 --> 00:57:28.820
Tourneys last longer.

480
00:57:30.572 --> 00:57:32.866
Baelon the brave.

481
00:57:32.950 --> 00:57:35.035
rider of vhagar.

482
00:57:35.118 --> 00:57:37.120
heir to the iron throne...

483
00:57:38.538 --> 00:57:40.540
Dead of a burst belly.

484
00:57:42.376 --> 00:57:43.877
The gods have a dark wit.

485
00:57:45.045 --> 00:57:46.672
It was a grim day.

486
00:57:48.256 --> 00:57:50.884
- I recall it all too well.
- Yeah...

487
00:57:51.885 --> 00:57:53.220
It was a good day for you.

488
00:57:55.222 --> 00:57:57.849
Jaehaerys named you hand
in baelon's stead.

489
00:58:01.186 --> 00:58:04.189
That's hardly how I viewed it.
your grace.

490
00:58:05.023 --> 00:58:06.650
It was a duty.

491
00:58:09.403 --> 00:58:13.198
You served my grandsire
nobly in his final days.

492
00:58:14.574 --> 00:58:16.827
You are the man
that taught me how to be king.

493
00:58:18.787 --> 00:58:20.789
You honor me. your grace.

494
00:58:22.958 --> 00:58:24.584
Just five days...

495
00:58:26.378 --> 00:58:29.589
You went from being another man
in jaehaerys's court.

496
00:58:29.673 --> 00:58:31.717
to the second most
powerful man in the realm.

497
00:58:33.010 --> 00:58:34.219
I wonder...

498
00:58:35.637 --> 00:58:38.432
How long did it take you
to choose yourself over your king?

499
00:58:41.476 --> 00:58:42.894
Your grace?

500
00:58:43.895 --> 00:58:46.523
I will never recover from aemma's death.

501
00:58:47.441 --> 00:58:48.650
But alicent...

502
00:58:49.651 --> 00:58:51.695
She took me
through the worst of my grief.

503
00:58:54.156 --> 00:58:56.158
She was a calculated distraction.

504
00:58:58.035 --> 00:59:01.371
I only now realize
how well-calculated it was.

505
00:59:01.455 --> 00:59:03.707
That is an absurdity.

506
00:59:04.291 --> 00:59:05.876
The queen loves you...

507
00:59:07.502 --> 00:59:09.504
As I know you love her.

508
00:59:09.588 --> 00:59:12.966
Your interests no longer align
with those of the realm.

509
00:59:13.050 --> 00:59:15.427
Yourjudgment has been compromised.

510
00:59:15.510 --> 00:59:18.013
A loyal hand must tell his king

511
00:59:18.096 --> 00:59:21.224
a discomforting truth
from time to time. your grace.

512
00:59:21.308 --> 00:59:22.476
If he doesn't...

513
00:59:24.311 --> 00:59:26.313
He's failed as a servant.

514
00:59:27.355 --> 00:59:29.733
You were a faithful servant. Otto.

515
00:59:39.326 --> 00:59:40.744
The crown and the realm

516
00:59:41.328 --> 00:59:44.331
both owe you a debt
that can never be repaid.

517
00:59:45.499 --> 00:59:48.085
But I can no longer trust your judgment.

518
01:00:12.526 --> 01:00:13.652
Come.

519
01:00:18.448 --> 01:00:21.451
I hope you can forgive
the late hour. Princess.

520
01:00:26.331 --> 01:00:29.334
I took great care in its preparation.

521
01:00:32.003 --> 01:00:34.881
If not brewed properly.
it can either prove ineffective

522
01:00:34.965 --> 01:00:39.052
- or else bear unpleasant...
- Brewed properly?

523
01:00:40.887 --> 01:00:42.514
